Diana Deedan Muyira (nke a na-akpọkarị naanị Deedan ma ọ bụ Miss Deedan), bụ onye Uganda na-eme ihe nkiri na onye mgbasa ozi, nke a maara maka ịrụ ọrụ Tracy Kintu na Nana Kagga's Beneath The Lies
A mụrụ Deedan na Kenya ma ọ kwaga Uganda ịrụ ọrụ.
Deedan bụ onye na-akwado nnukwu ememme egwu nke Kampala, Blankets and Wine kemgbe ọ malitere

O meela ọtụtụ ihe omume ndị ọzọ gụnyere Tokosa Food Fest Deedan bụ onye na-eme ihe ngosi redio na Radiocity Kampala ma na-akwado, ya na onye ọrụ ibe ya McKenzie, The Jam, ihe ngosi ụgbọala mgbede nke gosipụtara egwu na ozi maka Kampala.
O sonyeere ihe ngosi Urban Today n'afọ 2016 mgbe Gaetano Kagwa hapụrụ
N'afọ 2014, Deedan bidoro ọrụ ihe nkiri ya na Beneath The Lies, na-egwu Tracy Kintu, nwanyị si n'ezinụlọ bara ọgaranya nke na-eche mmetọ ụlọ site n'aka di ya.
